@startuml agent_dispatch_shadow_write
' Shadow-write phase of ADR 2026-05-16 (段階 1-4). This is the state on
' main as of PR #74: agent_dispatches gets written but never read; the
' existing /execute ndjson path still drives the assistant message
' lifecycle. The diagram is intentionally faithful to today's wire shape
' so reviewers can see "safe by default" — failures on the new path do
' not affect user-visible behavior.

title cc-tunnel: agent_dispatches shadow write (ADR 2026-05-16 段階 1-3, 実装済)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor User
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "cc-tunnel\n(SendMessage)" as T
database "PostgreSQL" as D
participant "ExecutionProvider\n(local / docker_gce)" as P
participant "cc-remote-agent" as A
participant "claude -p\n(subprocess)" as C

User -> F: メッセージ入力
F -> T: POST /conversations/{id}/messages

T -> D: SELECT conversation, messages (history)
T -> D: INSERT user message
T -> D: INSERT assistant message\n(status='streaming')
T -> D: INSERT agent_dispatches\n(status='pending')
note right of T: shadow write\n失敗は warn log のみ\nreader はまだ存在しない
T -> F: 202 Accepted {message_id}

== goroutine 内 (既存経路, 主) ==
T -> P: Execute(ctx, req, onEvent)
P -> A: POST /execute (JSON)
A -> C: fork/exec claude -p ...
C --> A: ndjson stream
A --> P: ndjson 転送

loop 2 秒間隔
  P --> T: onEvent(...) で集約
  T -> D: UPDATE messages\nSET message_data (content_blocks)
end

C --> A: exit
A --> P: stream 終了
P --> T: newSessionID

T -> D: UPDATE messages (final content_blocks,\n  session_id, cost_usd, ...)
T -> D: UPDATE messages SET status='completed'
T -> D: UPDATE conversations (title, status)
T -> D: UPDATE agent_dispatches\nSET status='consumed'

note over D
  agent_outputs テーブルへの書き込みは無い。
  cc-hook-bridge は image に同梱されているが、
  まだ PTY 常駐 claude が wire されていないので、
  /tmp/cc-hook-bridge-state.json も存在しない。
end note

@enduml
